v0.2.0:
  date: 2012-05-08
  changes:
    - Removed clearTarget (use grunt-contrib clean instead)
    - Added [almond](https://github.com/jrburke/almond) integration
    - Added automatic almond js module script tag replacement for html files
    - Improved documentation

